public interface Solution
A class that represents a solution for one of the questions / problems. Note that all classes that implement this interface will have the @SuppressWarnings("unused") annotation as they will be used at runtime via reflection (See Main.java for details).

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void exec()
    Runs the solution to the problem.
    String getName()
    Returns the header for the solution, which is the problem's name.
